## ⏱️ Complexity Analysis

Let `d` be the maximum number of digits (at most **9**).

### Time Complexity

There are only a fixed number of possible sequential digit numbers.

The algorithm generates at most:

```text id="5e1u5u"
8 + 7 + 6 + ... + 1 = 36
```

substrings.

Thus,

```text id="bqsdif"
O(1)
```

(Or equivalently **O(36)**.)

### Space Complexity

Ignoring the output array:

```text id="j2t9fr"
O(1)
```

